<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
	<% include common_headers.ejs %>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/index.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container" style='width:100%; padding-top:65px;'>
    <div class="jumbotron side_bar" style='width:100%;'>
	
		<% include navbar.ejs %>

		<div class="container" id="big_button_frame" style="text-align:center">
			<h1>
				<% if (game == 'wot') { %>
					World of Tanks Tactics
				<% } else if (game == 'wows') { %>
					World of Warships Tactics
				<% } else if (game == 'blitz') { %>
					World of Tanks Blitz Tactics
				<% } else if (game == 'aw') { %>
					Armored Warfare Tactics
				<% } %>	
			</h1>
			<p><span id="quote"></span></p>
			<p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="<%=game%>planner.html" id="new_room" role="button"><%= l('Create new room') %> &raquo;</a></p>
		</div>
	
	</div>

	<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-4">
		<h2>Welcome</h2>
		<p>This website is created to make tactical quick and easy. Just press the blue button, share the link with friends or not and get started. If you want the people you invite to be able to edit too, click on their name or the unlock button. There is more information in the getting started guide.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-4">
		<h2>Free and open</h2>
		<p>This website is free of charge, free of adds and open-source and I intend to keep it that way. There is however a donation button to cover hosting fees in the future.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-4">
		<h2>Some Statistics</h2>
		<p>Looks like this website is gaining a bit of popularity.  The last 30 days (from dec. 8) 10.830 unique tactics were created and 18.047 different users (# active sessions) have visited the website at least once. Thank you and keep spreading the word.</p>
	</div>

	</div>
	<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-4">
		<h2>Looking for translators</h2>
		<p>Thanks to some helpful people this website is already available in a few languages. If you want it available in your language too, get in touch. No technical skill required.</p>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
	
	<% include footer.ejs %>
	
	</div>
</body>
